      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstration that input parameters used in validation simulations are equivalent to those in the COU model, including geometric fidelity and material properties.",
      "rationale": "Validation simulations used nominal geometry from FDA benchmark CAD. COU device geometry includes manufacturing tolerances and surface roughness not present in benchmark model. Equivalency of input parameters between validation and COU contexts has not been formally demonstrated; not assessed."
