    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Following review of all 13 credibility factors, the team accepted the simulation evidence package for regulatory submission. Validation results generated under the current solver configuration demonstrate adequate agreement with experimental hemolysis data across the primary operating envelope. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification bounds are within acceptable limits for the intended submission scope. Remaining factor gaps are acknowledged and addressed through supplementary testing commitments.",
